abstract: If he can’t distinguish himself in New York City, how does he expect to do it on the national stage?
snippet: If he can’t distinguish himself in New York City, how does he expect to do it on the national stage?
lead_paragraph: I started this column from the elliptical machine. And why not? If Bill de Blasio can run New York City from my gym — the Prospect Park Y.M.C.A., 11-plus miles and roughly 40 minutes from Gracie Mansion — then why can’t I work there, too?

snippet: Though she was on the front lines helping to lead Signal Corps switchboard operators, she was not designated a veteran until after her death.
lead_paragraph: Overlooked is a series of obituaries about remarkable people whose deaths, beginning in 1851, went unreported in The Times.
